        the <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">American</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">population</ENAMEX>. If education and public policies are insufficient to promote
        behavioral changes to increase physical activity among most <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX>, can advances in
