        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">devices</ENAMEX>, or biological <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">agents</ENAMEX> designed to substitute for exercise.
        Many <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">individuals</ENAMEX> who otherwise would develop <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">diabetes</ENAMEX> or <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">cardiovascular disease</ENAMEX> would
